svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 20, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104tfs1665702791739.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tfs1665702791739.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tfs1665702791739.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"tfs1665702791739\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Structure Editor\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"tfs1665702791739__structure_editor_20835\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The Structure Editor enables you to define the contents of a main development object, including its sub objects.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tfs1665702791739__p_d5195e1_d5196e1_d5197e1\">It is located in the central editing area of the Define Structure worksheet of main object editors, such as a Entity Editor and Component Editor.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tfs1665702791739__p_d5198e1_d5199e1_d5200e1\">Typically, it displays a hierarchical table of the main\n         object and all its sub-objects, as well as selected object properties. It enables you to\n         add and delete development objects, and edit the listed properties. The properties\n         displayed depend on the object being edited.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tfs1665702791739__topic_d2667e1_d2668e1_d2669e1_d2670e1_d2671e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d743487e63\">\n                        \n How to\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tfs1665702791739__li_d2195e1_d2196e1_d2197e1\">To add objects to the main object structure, drag them from the Resource Browser and drop them on a valid target in the Structure Editor. You can also right-click and choose an <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Add</span> or <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Insert</span> option from the context menu.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tfs1665702791739__li_d2198e1_d2199e1_d2200e1\">To delete sub-objects, select the object that you\n               want to delete, right-click, and choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Delete</span>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tfs1665702791739__li_d2201e1_d2202e1_d2203e1\">To edit a property, click the property value, enter\n               a new value, and press <kbd class=\"ph userinput\">Enter</kbd>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tfs1665702791739__li_d2204e1_d2205e1_d2206e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kdb1665702780441.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kdb1665702780441.html\" title=\"You can resize the width of columns by clicking the triangle in column header, and setting the desired width.\">Resize Columns</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532334\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532334\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Structure Editor Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Structure Editor The Structure Editor enables you to define the contents of a main development object, including its sub objects. It is located in the central editing area of the Define Structure worksheet of main object editors, such as a Entity Editor and Component Editor. Typically, it displays a hierarchical table of the main object and all its sub-objects, as well as selected object properties. It enables you to add and delete development objects, and edit the listed properties. The properties displayed depend on the object being edited. How to To add objects to the main object structure, drag them from the Resource Browser and drop them on a valid target in the Structure Editor. You can also right-click and choose an Add or Insert option from the context menu. To delete sub-objects, select the object that you want to delete, right-click, and choose Delete . To edit a property, click the property value, enter a new value, and press Enter . Resize Columns Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}